snippet.title: Discover Neo4j AuraDB - S02E08
snippet.description:
We’re bringing back Discover Neo4j AuraDB to showcase all the powerful new features added to Aura! Whether you're a longtime user or just getting started, join us to see what’s new, how Aura makes graph databases easier than ever, and why now is the perfect time to try it out. 

Micheal Hunger: https://bsky.app/profile/mesirii.de
Neo4j AuraDB: https://dev.neo4j.com/discover-aura
Neo4j GraphAcademy: https://dev.neo4j.com/learn 


All previous episodes: https://neo4j.com/video/discover-aura-free-with-fun-datasets/

#neo4j #auradb #graphdatabase
